---
title: Double Caribbean Prawn & Veggie Couscous Bowl with Charred Corn Salsa & Aioli
description: The brown rice is so fluffy that it’s cuddling the fresh prawns in a warm hug. Let those flavours embrace you with Caribbean jerk seasoning and roast veggies with a zap of corn salsa and aioli drizzled over at the end.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

*We’ve replaced the couscous in this recipe with pearl couscous due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
